data.description: 'CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS' Charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home with 1,131 sqft of space, offered at an affordable price. Step inside to discover updated hardwood floors in the main living areas, complemented by a cozy wood-burning fireplace in the spacious living room. The bedrooms feature new carpeting, and the bathroom boasts tasteful finishes with tongue and groove ceilings. The large kitchen is perfect for creating your family's favorite meals. This well-maintained home includes a 2011-installed metal roof, a new hot water heater, and an HVAC system from 2015. Enjoy the generous backyard, complete with a pear tree, pecan tree, and a secure fence for your privacy. Perfect for those seeking comfort and value in a home.
